Blacknightmare:

"We have an intruder, Blaze" replied the femme "Well, intruder, " 
said the femme "show you and we don't harm you, and perhaps we can 
have an agreement..."

All the base internal defences turned on while the door locked down.

Blacknightmare sked in low voice to Kitkat and Blaze "can you smell 
his or her scent???"
